@startuml
title Gambar 5.17 Sequence Diagram Peta Interaktif

actor User
participant "Map Page" as MapPage
participant "Peta API" as PetaAPI
database "Aset Model" as AsetModel

User -> MapPage: Membuka halaman peta
MapPage -> PetaAPI: GET /api/peta/markers
PetaAPI -> AsetModel: Mengambil data aset dan koordinat
AsetModel --> PetaAPI: Data marker aset
PetaAPI --> MapPage: Marker dan layer peta
User -> MapPage: Memilih marker aset
MapPage -> PetaAPI: GET /api/peta/detail/:id
PetaAPI -> AsetModel: Mengambil detail aset
AsetModel --> PetaAPI: Detail aset
PetaAPI --> MapPage: Detail aset
MapPage --> User: Menampilkan detail aset

@enduml
